snippet.textDisplay: This may be his best song. If this is a sign of what's to come then I'm definitely excited to hear his next project. At first I didn't understand the hype from this guy but after listening to all three of his albums and this song I'm a fan. It's simple and most of the songs are less than 2 minutes but I think it would be weird if they were longer. Some of his lyrics are stupid but it's just fun music and he's got a unique sound. I kept thinking that it would be better if he had some features, but I'm not really sure who would fit well with his style. Also I've never heard him do a future. His music just gets everybody turned up and that's what people need sometimes.
